highlights.text: KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Top Songs Germany. “Golden” is the highest at #1.
“Andere Niveau” by Bobby Vandamme, 3robi, and Chahid is the highest new entry on Top Songs Germany at #3.
“Another Love” by Tom Odell has been on Top Songs Germany the longest, at 232 weeks straight.
“Timeless (feat Playboi Carti)” by The Weeknd and Playboi Carti is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Germany, up 90 spots at #96.
